OL,4,CAsda to allow permanent hybrid working
OL,5,Cfor offices
OL,6, Asda has announced it will make hybrid
OL,7, working permanent at its head offices
OL,8, once Covid restrictions are lifted.
OL,10,FThe supermarket group said staff at
OL,11,FAsda House in Leeds and George House in
OL,12,FLeicester can choose where they work.
OL,14,FAround 4,000 staff work at both
OL,15,Foffices, with the majority based in
OL,16,FLeeds.
OL,18,FEngland is set to lift final Covid
OL,19,Fmeasures on 19 July and many businesses
OL,20,Fhave indicated they will continue to
OL,21,Fallow flexible working.
